Name: One Hundred Times Me

One Hundred Times Me is a game where you are your own greatest enemy. The basic objective of One Hundred Times Me is pretty simple: destroy demons on every round in less than 30 seconds. But here is a twist - your every move of all the rounds youâ€™ve beaten is recorded and played back by your past selves. With each round the board gets more and more crowded.
